---
import FeatureLayout from '../../layouts/FeatureLayout.astro';
---

<FeatureLayout
  title="Chat interna operatori sala giochi · GestHall Suite"
  description="Messaggistica in tempo reale tra tutti gli operatori. Testo, immagini, messaggi vocali ed emoji. Gruppi e messaggi diretti con indicatore di digitazione."
  tag="Chat interna"
  heading="Tutti gli operatori connessi in tempo reale."
  sub="Messaggistica istantanea tra tutto il personale. Testo, immagini, vocali ed emoji. Gruppi tematici, messaggi diretti, indicatore di digitazione."
  plan="suite"
  related={['app-mobile', 'turni', 'white-label']}
>

  <div slot="visual" class="feat-mock-card" style="width:100%">
    <div class="fmc-header">
      <span class="fmc-title">Chat · #generale</span>
      <span class="ch-online">3 online</span>
    </div>
    <div class="ch-body">
      <div class="ch-msg ch-in">
        <div class="ch-avatar ch-av-a">MR</div>
        <div class="ch-bubble-wrap">
          <div class="ch-sender">Marco Rossi</div>
          <div class="ch-bubble">Hai chiuso il turno serale?</div>
          <div class="ch-time">22:01</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="ch-msg ch-out">
        <div class="ch-bubble-wrap ch-bubble-wrap-out">
          <div class="ch-bubble ch-bubble-out">Sì, versamento fatto ✓</div>
          <div class="ch-time">22:03</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="ch-msg ch-in">
        <div class="ch-avatar ch-av-b">SM</div>
        <div class="ch-bubble-wrap">
          <div class="ch-sender">Silvia Martini</div>
          <div class="ch-bubble ch-voice-bubble">
            <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 1a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v3a2 2 0 0 1-4 0V3a2 2 0 0 1 2-2z"/><path d="M2 7a4 4 0 0 0 8 0M6 11v1"/></svg>
            <span class="ch-vbar"></span><span class="ch-vbar"></span>
            <span class="ch-vbar"></span><span class="ch-vbar"></span>
            <span class="ch-vtime">0:08</span>
          </div>
          <div class="ch-time">22:05</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="ch-typing">
        <div class="ch-avatar ch-av-c">LF</div>
        <div class="ch-typing-dots">
          <span></span><span></span><span></span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="ch-input-row">
      <div class="ch-input">Scrivi un messaggio…</div>
      <div class="ch-input-icons">
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="7" cy="7" r="6"/><path d="M4.5 8.5s.5 1.5 2.5 1.5 2.5-1.5 2.5-1.5M5 5.5h.01M9 5.5h.01"/></svg>
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M7 1a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v4a3 3 0 0 0 6 0V4a3 3 0 0 0-3-3z"/><path d="M2 8a5 5 0 0 0 10 0M7 13v1"/></svg>
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="1" y="1" width="12" height="10" rx="2"/><path d="M4 5h6M4 8h4"/></svg>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <Fragment slot="steps">
    <div class="fp-step">
      <div class="fp-step-num">1</div>
      <div class="fp-step-title">Apri una conversazione</div>
      <div class="fp-step-desc">La chat è accessibile dalla sidebar in tutte le pagine dell'app. Gruppi tematici (es. "#generale", "#turni") e messaggi diretti tra operatori, senza uscire dal gestionale.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="fp-step">
      <div class="fp-step-num">2</div>
      <div class="fp-step-title">Invia testo, immagini o vocali</div>
      <div class="fp-step-desc">Scrivi un messaggio, allega una foto (compressione automatica client-side) o registra un messaggio vocale tenendo premuto il microfono. L'anteprima audio è disponibile prima dell'invio.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="fp-step">
      <div class="fp-step-num">3</div>
      <div class="fp-step-title">Ricevi notifiche push</div>
      <div class="fp-step-desc">I nuovi messaggi in chat arrivano come notifiche push sul dispositivo anche con l'app chiusa. L'indicatore "sta scrivendo" è visibile in tempo reale.</div>
    </div>
  </Fragment>

  <Fragment slot="benefits">
    <div class="fp-benefit-list">
      <div class="fp-benefit">
        <div class="fp-benefit-icon"></div>
        <div class="fp-benefit-text"><strong>Messaggi vocali integrati.</strong> Registra e invia audio fino a 5 MB direttamente dalla chat. Utile per comunicazioni rapide senza digitare.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="fp-benefit">
        <div class="fp-benefit-icon"></div>
        <div class="fp-benefit-text"><strong>Emoji picker con 250 emoji.</strong> Panel emoji a categorie integrato nel campo di testo. Si inserisce alla posizione del cursore.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="fp-benefit">
        <div class="fp-benefit-icon"></div>
        <div class="fp-benefit-text"><strong>Immagini con compressione automatica.</strong> Le foto vengono ridimensionate e compresse client-side (max 1200 px, WebP) prima dell'invio. Nessun file enorme da gestire.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="fp-benefit">
        <div class="fp-benefit-icon"></div>
        <div class="fp-benefit-text"><strong>Senza app esterne.</strong> La chat è dentro il gestionale. Nessun WhatsApp, nessun gruppo Telegram da gestire fuori dall'app di lavoro.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Fragment>

</FeatureLayout>

<style>
.ch-online { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; color: oklch(0.48 0.18 155); background: oklch(96% 0.05 155); padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 99px }
.ch-body { padding: 14px 16px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; min-height: 180px }
.ch-msg { display: flex; align-items: flex-end; gap: 8px }
.ch-out { flex-direction: row-reverse }
.ch-avatar { width: 26px; height: 26px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 9px; font-weight: 700; color: oklch(97% 0.005 245); flex-shrink: 0 }
.ch-av-a { background: linear-gradient(135deg, oklch(0.65 0.14 168), oklch(0.55 0.18 200)) }
.ch-av-b { background: linear-gradient(135deg, oklch(0.65 0.14 250), oklch(0.55 0.18 280)) }
.ch-av-c { background: linear-gradient(135deg, oklch(0.65 0.14 60),  oklch(0.55 0.18 40)) }
.ch-bubble-wrap { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 3px; max-width: 76% }
.ch-bubble-wrap-out { align-items: flex-end }
.ch-sender { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--faint) }
.ch-bubble { font-size: 12px; padding: 7px 10px; border-radius: 12px; background: var(--surface-2); color: var(--text); border-bottom-left-radius: 3px; line-height: 1.4 }
.ch-bubble-out { background: oklch(0.72 0.16 168 / 0.15); color: oklch(0.38 0.14 168); border-bottom-left-radius: 12px; border-bottom-right-radius: 3px }
.ch-voice-bubble { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px; padding: 7px 10px }
.ch-voice-bubble svg { flex-shrink: 0; color: var(--accent) }
.ch-vbar { display: inline-block; width: 3px; border-radius: 2px; background: var(--accent); animation: cv-bar 1.2s ease-in-out infinite }
.ch-vbar:nth-child(2) { height: 10px; animation-delay: 0s }
.ch-vbar:nth-child(3) { height: 15px; animation-delay: .15s }
.ch-vbar:nth-child(4) { height: 8px; animation-delay: .3s }
.ch-vbar:nth-child(5) { height: 12px; animation-delay: .1s }
@keyframes cv-bar { 0%,100%{transform:scaleY(.4);opacity:.5} 50%{transform:scaleY(1);opacity:1} }
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) { .ch-vbar { animation: none; opacity: .6 } }
.ch-vtime { font-size: 10px; color: var(--muted); margin-left: 2px }
.ch-time { font-size: 9px; color: var(--faint) }
.ch-typing { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px }
.ch-typing-dots { display: flex; gap: 3px; align-items: center; background: var(--surface-2); border-radius: 12px; border-bottom-left-radius: 3px; padding: 8px 12px }
.ch-typing-dots span { width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--faint); animation: ct 1.1s ease-in-out infinite }
.ch-typing-dots span:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: .18s }
.ch-typing-dots span:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: .36s }
@keyframes ct { 0%,100%{transform:scaleY(.5);opacity:.4} 50%{transform:scaleY(1);opacity:1} }
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) { .ch-typing-dots span { animation: none; opacity: .6 } }
.ch-input-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; padding: 10px 16px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border-sub) }
.ch-input { flex: 1; font-size: 12px; color: var(--faint); background: var(--surface); border-radius: 20px; padding: 7px 12px; border: 1px solid var(--border-sub) }
.ch-input-icons { display: flex; gap: 8px; color: var(--faint) }
</style>
